{"tid":883816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透死全家]南極罕見爆發謀殺案　科學家被「劇透」怒砍同事","createTime":"2018-10-31T06:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T06:24:44.000Z","uid":20032,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"743135555231d3256a1ed60e4ba7bcb8e4657dbd","tid":883816,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/10/31/99/5466996.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F99%2F5466996.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=512961f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南極罕見謀殺案！在南極洲偏遠基地工作的科學家謝爾蓋（Sergey Savitsky），日前用菜刀攻擊同事奧列格（Oleg Beloguzov），使得奧列格心臟受損仍在重症看護中，而謝爾蓋行兇的原因，竟然是自己閱讀書籍被對方「劇透」揭露結局。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，謝爾蓋在南極洲的研究工作相當艱苦，只能依靠閱讀來娛樂，然而奧列格不斷地透露書籍中之後的情節，使得謝爾蓋相當憤怒才會行兇。目前謝爾蓋因涉嫌謀殺未遂，被拘留在俄羅斯聖彼得堡。報導中指出，這應該是南極洲首次有人被控謀殺。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181030/1457217/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181030%2F1457217%2F&d=THuf5Gc%2FlHAsI2zGJgWxlvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=3fa710c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181030%2F1457217%2F&h=f1cae507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181030/1457217/</a>"},{"pid":"de1b6fb183ba31ea2bfd830c3f6437d6385dd4f1","tid":883816,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ba13b7506f1fa23558425657360f3c41ad4f20","tid":883816,"uid":28775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/883291\" data-auto-link target=\"